  "suggestion": ["The term 'Adaptive Systems' should be revised to 'Adaptive Instructional Systems' for consistency with similar approved IEEE PAR documents.", "Revised Version: 'Recommended Practice for Ethically Aligned Design of Artificial Intelligence in Adaptive Instructional Systems'"]
}}

Note: "Artificial Intelligence" remains as full text without adding "(AI)" abbreviation.
